<title>USA: Chromatics Color Q1 net loss widens.</title>
<headline>Chromatics Color Q1 net loss widens.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Three months ended</p>
<p>							    March 31,</p>
<p>						   1997		 1996</p>
<p> REVENUES				     58,700	     54,600</p>
<p> NET LOSS				  1,043,400	    862,600</p>
<p>WEIGHTED AVERAGE NUMBER OF</p>
<p>COMMON SHARES AND EQUIVALENTS</p>
<p>  OUTSTANDING			    7,253,957	  4,760,300</p>
<p> NET LOSS PER SHARE			   0.14		 0.18</p>
<p>NOTE: company said Q1 1997 net loss was due to increased expenses relating to its long-range business plan to seek commercial applications of its intellectual properties and technologies in the medical field.</p>
<p>Full name is Chromatics Color Sciences International Inc.</p>
